'''Canadian football''' is a form of [[gridiron football]] played almost exclusively in [[Canada]] in which two teams of 12 players each compete for territorial control of a field of play {{convert|110|yd|m|0}} long and {{convert|65|yd|m|0}} wide&lt;!--
NOTE TO EDITORS

